essions all still running. All statuses match. `updatedAt` timestamps advancing normally (no stall).\nSystem: \nSystem: **No state transitions. No new failures. No blockers.**\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent exit.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:49:12 UTC] Comparing current state (15:46 UTC) against baseline (15:30 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Baseline:** `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ `cron:e7885813` ✅ `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ `telegram:group:-5168104492` ✅ `telegram:direct:6053576134` ✅ `main` ✅\nSystem: \nSystem: **Current:** All 7 sessions match baseline exactly — same statuses, `updatedAt` advancing normally, no failures, no blockers, no new sessions, no zombies changed.\nSystem: \nSystem: **No state transitions detected. Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:50:32 UTC] Comparing current state (15:49 UTC) against baseline (15:30 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: **Baseline:** `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ `cron:e7885813` ✅ `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ `telegram:group:-5168104492` ✅ `telegram:direct:6053576134` ✅ `main` ✅\nSystem: \nSystem: **Current:** All 7 sessions match baseline exactly — same statuses, no failures, no blockers, no new sessions, no zombies changed.\nSystem: \nSystem: **No state transitions detected. Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:53:00 UTC] State stable vs baseline. Silent.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:55:14 UTC] **Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:59:42 UTC] Silent. All sessions match baseline — no new failures, no blockers, no state transitions since 15:30 UTC.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 16:02:56 UTC] Silent. All sessions match baseline — no new failures, no blockers, no state transitions since last check.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBE